### Genfeed API - Agent Thread Resource Endpoints
### Canonical namespace: /agent/threads.

########################################
# Threads
########################################

### List Agent Threads
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/agent/threads?status=active
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Create Agent Thread
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/agent/threads
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Operator Planning",
  "source": "web"
}


### Get Agent Thread
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/agent/threads/{{testAgentThreadId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Update Agent Thread
PATCH {{apiBaseUrl}}/agent/threads/{{testAgentThreadId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Operator Planning",
  "isPinned": true
}


### Archive All Active Agent Threads (mass-by-filter bulk update)
PATCH {{apiBaseUrl}}/agent/threads
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "archived"
}


########################################
# Messages
########################################

### List Thread Messages
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/agent/threads/{{testAgentThreadId}}/messages?limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Get Thread Message
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/agent/threads/{{testAgentThreadId}}/messages/{{testAgentMessageId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Add Thread Message
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/agent/threads/{{testAgentThreadId}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Manual note on this thread.",
  "role": "user"
}
